::Aerotaur::

"Aw now you don't want to do that.  Why don't you come with me for a while?  
And my name is Aerotaur."  At that moment he sees a chip headed for Trinity, 
still in his arms, and leaps forward the chip missing his tail by mere 
inches.  After this he looks down and says "It isn't safe here we're leaving 
now.  Who are your parents?  Where should I take you?"
